caption: Table 1: Results on WebVision dataset.
description: This table presents the results of experiments conducted on the WebVision dataset using different methods. The methods evaluated include SSR, EntSel, SSR + EntSel, DivideMix, EntSel, and DivideMix + EntSel. The table shows the accuracy and ROC AUC scores achieved by each method.  The results demonstrate the impact of different methods and their combinations on both classification accuracy and open-set detection performance in a real-world dataset.
